{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01UGHHMLdqqAuz1qD79Ho8ze","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All Phase 1 features are built. Here's a summary of what was done:\n\n### Schema (SQLite)\n- Updated `src-tauri/migrations/001_initial_schema.sql` with all tables: `accounts`, `budget_series`, `sub_series`, `import_batches`, `transactions`, `transaction_splits`, `monthly_budget`, `recurring_transactions`, `projects`, `project_items`, `tags`, `transaction_tags`, `categorization_rules` + all indexes\n\n### Backend (Rust)\n- Fixed `lib.rs` to remove non-existent command references\n- Schema uses `include_str!` for clean migration management\n\n### Frontend Stores\n- **`db.ts`** — `query<T>()` and `execute()` helpers wrapping `tauri-plugin-sql`\n- **`accounts.ts`** — Full CRUD with `$state` reactivity\n- **`transactions.ts`** — CRUD + search/filter + auto-categorization (learns patterns via `categorization_rules`)\n- **`budget.ts`** — Series CRUD + monthly budget upsert + budget view aggregation (planned vs actual)\n\n### Types (`src/lib/types/index.ts`)\n- All entity interfaces: `Account`, `Transaction`, `BudgetSeries`, `MonthlyBudget`, `BudgetLineItem`, `ImportBatch`, `CategorizationRule`, `Project`, `ProjectItem`, `DashboardSummary`\n\n### Pages\n- **Dashboard** — Live summary cards (balance, income, expenses, count), account list, recent transactions, budget progress bars\n- **Accounts** — List with balances, create/edit modal, soft delete\n- **Transactions** — Table with search, account/category filters, inline categorization dropdown, create/edit modal\n- **Budget** — Month navigation, series grouped by budget area, inline editable planned amounts, progress bars (color-coded: green/yellow/red)\n\n### Prerequisites\nYou need to install system dependencies before `cargo build`:\n```bash\nsudo apt-get install -y libgtk-3-dev libwebkit2gtk-4.1-dev librsvg2-dev\n```\n\nThen run with `npm run tauri dev`."}],"s